&lt;p&gt;Current technologies help to&nbsp;increase success rates in&nbsp;the IVF treatment programs in&nbsp;some cases up&nbsp;to&nbsp;50% and more. Chances are higher in&nbsp;women under 35. In&nbsp;any case, the procedure is&nbsp;safe and can be&nbsp;repeated many times until the wished result is&nbsp;achieved.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;In&nbsp;what cases is&nbsp;IVF indicated?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The procedure is&nbsp;indicated if&nbsp;there is&nbsp;no&nbsp;other way to&nbsp;treat infertility:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;non-patent fallopian tubes due to&nbsp;their pathology;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;no&nbsp;fallopian tubes;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;no&nbsp;ovulation or&nbsp;small number of&nbsp;eggs and their low quality;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;no&nbsp;uterus or&nbsp;ovaries;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;small number of&nbsp;motile or&nbsp;morphologically normal sperm in&nbsp;a&nbsp;male partner;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;confirmed endometriosis;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;sexual disorders that prevent conception.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;IVF is&nbsp;also possible in&nbsp;the case of&nbsp;serious hereditary diseases in&nbsp;the history: during the treatment program the embryos will be&nbsp;tested and only healthy embryos will be&nbsp;transferred into the uterine cavity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Where to&nbsp;do&nbsp;IVF in&nbsp;Saint-Petersburg?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;IVF is&nbsp;just one infertility treatment program. Our International Centre for Reproductive Medicine (ICRM) practices different methods and technologies: stimulated and natural cycle IVF, ICSI, PGT, assisted hatching and other procedures. The key to&nbsp;success is&nbsp;having full information. Before the treatment program, the doctor will administer a&nbsp;number of&nbsp;tests for both partners. Based on&nbsp;the data received, the specialist will determine what treatment program will fit your needs best to&nbsp;help you conceive and give birth to&nbsp;the baby, and will inform you of&nbsp;the costs of&nbsp;your treatment.&lt;/p&gt;";s:10:"prices_url";s:40:"/prices-and-actions/prices/#ivf-programs";s:12:"prices_title";s:11:"More prices";s:7:"picture";a:10:{s:8:"ORIGINAL";s:26:"/upload/iblock/079/eco.png";s:13:"webp_ORIGINAL";s:49:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/079/0_0_1_95/eco.webp";s:12:"main_complex";s:26:"/upload/iblock/079/eco.png";s:17:"webp_main_complex";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/079/114_114_1_95/eco.webp";s:14:"services_index";s:26:"/upload/iblock/079/eco.png";s:19:"webp_services_index";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/079/114_114_1_95/eco.webp";s:8:"category";s:26:"/upload/iblock/079/eco.png";s:13:"webp_category";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/079/114_114_1_95/eco.webp";s:6:"prices";s:26:"/upload/iblock/079/eco.png";s:11:"webp_prices";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/079/114_114_1_95/eco.webp";}s:24:"showServiceTypesOnPrices";b:0;s:21:"servicesForPricesPage";a:3:{i:3929;a:86:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"3929";s:4:"NAME";s:13:"IVF with ICSI";s:4:"CODE";s:13:"ivf-with-icsi";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:148:"IVF with egg fertilization by ICSI method (injection of one thoroughly selected sperm into egg cytoplasm with the help of special micro instruments)";s:11:"DETAIL_TEXT";s:431:"<p>
