	 In&nbsp;ICRM, experienced specialists will perform ICSI in&nbsp;a&nbsp;professional way, will help you to&nbsp;achieve pregnancy and give birth to&nbsp;a&nbsp;healthy baby.
</p>";s:15:"DETAIL_PAGE_URL";s:51:"/services/ivf-programs/natural-cycle-ivf-with-icsi/";s:17:"IBLOCK_SECTION_ID";s:3:"188";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:28:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE";a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:913:"&lt;p&gt;In&nbsp;standard IVF protocols, hormonal ovarian stimulation is&nbsp;used to&nbsp;collect quality oocytes and perform IntraCytoplasmic Sperm Injection. Intake of&nbsp;gonadotropic hormones causes maturation of&nbsp;several follicles, so&nbsp;your doctor can retrieve more than one oocyte using ovarian puncture. If&nbsp;ICSI is&nbsp;done in&nbsp;a&nbsp;Natural Cycle IVF, ovarian stimulation is&nbsp;not necessary. One oocyte matures in&nbsp;a&nbsp;natural way, and it&nbsp;is&nbsp;retrieved on&nbsp;the ovulation day in&nbsp;order to&nbsp;insert a&nbsp;sperm into&nbsp;it. Such protocol is&nbsp;indicated in&nbsp;the following cases:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;antisperm antibodies in&nbsp;a&nbsp;woman;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;blockage of&nbsp;fallopian tubes;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;male infertility;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;contraindications to&nbsp;hormonal therapy.&lt;/li&gt;
