  &lt;li&gt;ICRM has its own bank of egg donors. They are women under 35 having at least one healthy baby and examined in accordance with the Russian medical legislation.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Every egg donor undergoes full medical examination in accordance with the Russian law as well additional examination by our genetic specialist and psychologist.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;All eggs retrieved from the donor chosen by you, regardless of their quantity, will be your property at a fixed price.&lt;/li&gt;
